text: VfB Stuttgart is the name of a football club in Germany. The club was founded in 1893 and won the German championship five times (1950, 1952, 1984, 1992, 2007). ==League position== Season League Position 2000/01 Bundesliga 15th 2001/02 Bundesliga 8th 2002/03 Bundesliga 2nd 2003/04 Bundesliga 4th 2004/05 Bundesliga 5th 2005/06 Bundesliga 9th 2006/07 Bundesliga Champions 2007/08 Bundesliga 6th 2008/09 Bundesliga 3rd ===Former position=== ==References== Category:Fußball-Bundesliga Category:Football clubs in Baden-Württemberg Category:Stuttgart Category:1893 establishments in Europe Category:1890s establishments in Germany
